"{\"uid\": \"wishtv.com-news-local-news-10th-annual-cop-on-a-rooftop-raises-money-for-special-olympics-at-area-dunkin-donuts\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"INDIANAPOLIS (WISH) - Area law enforcement and Dunkin' Donuts stores are teaming up with Special Olympics Indiana for the 10th annual\\\"Cop on a Rooftop\\\" on Friday.The event raised $145,000 for Special Olympics Indiana in its first eight years.As the name suggests, police officers with theLaw Enforcement Torch Runwill station themselves on top of participating Dunkin' Donuts across the state, to call attention to the stores.Then other officers on the ground will ask for donations in the drive-thru and in-store.Plainfield Police Department Assistant Chief says it's important for law enforcement to be involved.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 614, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 14, \"end\": 18, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/WISH-TV\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.7431758247189058e-17, \"text\": \"WISH\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/WISH-TV\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/WISH-TV\"}, {\"begin\": 47, \"end\": 54, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Dunkin'_Donuts\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Dunkin'\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Dunkin'_Donuts\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Dunkin'_Donuts\"}, {\"begin\": 106, \"end\": 113, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Indiana\", \"score\": 0.9999984036693612, \"rank\": 1.5106006424427738e-06, \"text\": \"Indiana\", \"types\": [\"Q3455524\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Indiana\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Indiana\"}, {\"begin\": 361, \"end\": 368, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Dunkin'_Donuts\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Dunkin'\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Dunkin'_Donuts\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Dunkin'_Donuts\"}, {\"begin\": 525, \"end\": 542, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/New_York_City_Police_Department\", \"score\": 0.982579954999253, \"rank\": 0.017109105251477585, \"text\": \"Police Department\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/New_York_City_Police_Department\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/New_York_City_Police_Department\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"We got to be out in the community talking to people, building relationships and this is just one way we do it,\\\" hen you have the uh the whole stigma with the cops and the donuts, that thing that started a long time ago, but I do not think you will have, you will see our officers eating donuts here today.According to Special Olympics Indiana, all the donations go directly to support athletes with intellectual disabilities in Indiana, including being able to offer programming for free.CEO Jeff Mohler says the event also serves as a great way to spread awareness of the nonprofit.\", \"from\": 614, \"to\": 1198, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 933, \"end\": 949, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Special_Olympics\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.2527219501635285e-16, \"text\": \"Special Olympics\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Special_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Special_Olympics\"}, {\"begin\": 950, \"end\": 957, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Indiana\", \"score\": 0.9999984036693612, \"rank\": 1.5106006424427738e-06, \"text\": \"Indiana\", \"types\": [\"Q3455524\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Indiana\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Indiana\"}, {\"begin\": 1043, \"end\": 1050, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Indiana\", \"score\": 0.9999984036693612, \"rank\": 1.5106006424427738e-06, \"text\": \"Indiana\", \"types\": [\"Q3455524\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Indiana\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/re